p: The title compound was obtained in 45% yield from compound 33 following the general procedure for Suzuki arylation: 1H NMR (300 MHz, CDCl 3) δ 3.91 (s, 3H), 4.66 (s, 2H), 6.62 (dd, J = 0.9, 7.5 Hz, 1H), 7.16 (dd, J = 0.9, 8.4 Hz, 1H), 7.38 (t, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.50–7.56 (m, 3H), 7.62 (d, J = 7.2 Hz, 1H), 7.73 (td, J = 1.5, 7.7 Hz, 1H), 7.85 (td, J = 1.2, 7.8 Hz, 1H), 8.02 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 8.31 (d, J = 2.1 Hz, 1H), 8.90 (d, J = 2.4 Hz, 1H).
